Jean Sincere https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jean_Sincere 0 Jean Sincere "Sinny" Zambello (August 16, 1919 – April 3, 2013) was an American film, television, theater and voice actress. Her credits included the films Roxanne and The Incredibles, as well as recent roles in the television musical, Glee.
